# ðŸ“Š Sales Performance Dashboard

## ðŸ“ Project Overview
This project presents an **interactive Power BI dashboard** built using the *Global Superstore* dataset.  
The goal was to explore sales and profitability trends across regions, categories, and time periods to identify opportunities for business optimization.

---

## ðŸŽ¯ Business Objective
To provide insights that help management:
- Understand key sales and profit trends.
- Identify top-performing and underperforming products and regions.
- Discover areas for improvement in discount strategy and profit margin.
- Support data-driven decision-making.

---

## ðŸ“‚ Dataset
- **Source:** [Global Superstore Dataset](https://github.com/yannie28/Global-Superstore/blob/master/Global_Superstore%28CSV%29.csv)
- **Format:** CSV
- **Size:** ~50,000 records
- **Key Columns:**
  - `Order Date`, `Ship Date`, `Category`, `Sub-Category`, `Region`, `Sales`, `Profit`, `Discount`, `Quantity`, `Customer Name`, `Segment`.

---

## âš™ï¸ Tools & Techniques
- **Power BI** â€” Data modelling, DAX calculations, and visualization.  
- **Excel** â€” Preliminary data cleaning and exploration.  
- **Power Query** â€” Data transformation.  
- **KPIs Used:**
  - Total Sales  
  - Total Profit  
  - Profit Margin  
  - Average Discount  
  - Total Orders  

---

## ðŸ“ˆ Visualizations
| Visualization | Type | Description |
|----------------|------|--------------|
| Total Sales, Profit, Margin | KPI Cards | Key business metrics |
| Sales & Profit over Time | Line Chart | Monthly/Yearly performance |
| Profit by Region | Map / Bar Chart | Geographic breakdown |
| Top 10 Products by Profit | Horizontal Bar | Identify best performers |
| Profit Margin by Category | Column Chart | Compare profitability |
| Discount vs Profit | Scatter Plot | Understand impact of discounts |

